Remy Dufrene, 3, of Raceland, Louisiana, was in the kitchen with his grandmother when he ran out the back door as she was pouring milk .
The old woman tried to chase after him but soon there was a loud scream as he fell into the drainage ditch .
Emergency workers spent almost an hour trying to resuscitate the boy but it took him 15 minutes to find his body .
'As soon as I pulled him out, his pour little belly looked like it was full of water,' said the boy's father .